claim.claim-text:
A mechanical system (1), forming a cam follower or a rocker arm, the mechanical system (1) comprising:
- a support element (10);
- a pin (30) extending between two opposite ends (35, 36) along a first axis (X1) and supported by the support element (10); and
- a roller (40) movable in rotation relative to the pin (30) around the first axis (X1) and adapted to roll on a cam (2);
wherein the pin (30) and/or the roller (40) is provided with at least one recess (38; 48; 38, 48; 138; 38a, 38b, 38c; 48a, 48b, 48c) forming a lubricant reservoir at an interface (60) between the pin (30) and the roller (40).
